{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id6c35a8eb-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2225"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2225"},"text":"§ 2225.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Credit or reimbursement","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id6c35a8ec-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2225/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Requests for credits","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"With respect to an authorized flood damage reduction project, or separable element thereof, that has been constructed by a non-Federal interest under section 701b–13 ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002099"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn002099"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" See References in Text note below."}],"tail":" of this title, or an authorized coastal navigation project that has been constructed by the Corps of Engineers pursuant to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t33/s561"},"text":"section 561 of this title","children":[],"tail":" before "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2018-10-23"},"text":"October 23, 2018","children":[],"tail":", the Secretary may provide to the non-Federal interest, at the request of the non-Federal interest, a credit in an amount equal to the estimated Federal share of the cost of the project or separable element, in lieu of providing to the non-Federal interest a reimbursement in that amount or reimbursement of funds of an equivalent amount, subject to the availability of appropriations."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id6c35a8ed-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2225/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Application of credits","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"At the request of the non-Federal interest, the Secretary may apply all or a portion of such credit to the share of the cost of the non-Federal interest of carrying out other flood damage reduction and coastal navigation projects or studies.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id6c35a8ee-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s2225/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Application of reimbursement","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"At the request of the non-Federal interest, the Secretary may apply such funds, subject to the availability of appropriations, equal to the share of the cost of the non-Federal interest of carrying out other flood damage reduction and coastal navigation projects or studies.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id6c35a8ef-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/121/tI/s1022"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–121, title I, § 1022","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2014-06-10"},"text":"June 10, 2014","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/128/1228"},"text":"128 Stat. 1228","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/322/tI/s1171"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–322, title I, § 1171","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2016-12-16"},"text":"Dec. 16, 2016","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/130/1671"},"text":"130 Stat. 1671","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/270/tI/s1136/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–270, title I, § 1136(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2018-10-23"},"text":"Oct. 23, 2018","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/132/3783"},"text":"132 Stat. 3783","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id6c35a8f0-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id6c35a8f1-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id6c35a8f2-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t33/s701b–13"},"text":"Section 701b–13 of this title","children":[],"tail":", referred to in subsec. (a), was repealed by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/121/tI"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–121, title I","children":[],"tail":", §1014(c)(3), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2014-06-10"},"text":"June 10, 2014","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/128/1222"},"text":"128 Stat. 1222","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"id6c35a8f3-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2018—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/270"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–270","children":[],"tail":" amended section generally. Prior to amendment, section related to credit in lieu of reimbursement."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2016—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/322/s1171/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–322, § 1171(1)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “for which a written agreement with the Corps of Engineers for construction was finalized on or before "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2014-12-31"},"text":"December 31, 2014","children":[],"tail":", under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t33/s701b–13"},"text":"section 701b–13 of this title","children":[],"tail":" (as it existed before the repeal made by section 1014(c)(3))” for “that has been constructed by a non-Federal interest under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t33/s701b–13"},"text":"section 701b–13 of this title","children":[],"tail":" before "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2014-06-10"},"text":"June 10, 2014","children":[],"tail":"”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/322/s1171/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–322, § 1171(2)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “non-Federal share of the cost of carrying out other water resources development projects or studies of the non-Federal interest” for “share of the cost of the non-Federal interest of carrying out other flood damage reduction projects or studies”."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"id6c35a8f4-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section was enacted as part of the Water Resources Reform and Development Act of 2014, and not as part of the Water Resources Development Act of 1986 which comprises this chapter.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"id6c35a8f5-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"miscellaneous","id":"id6c35a8f6-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"“Secretary” Defined","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Secretary means the Secretary of the Army, see ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/121/s2"},"text":"section 2 of Pub. L. 113–121","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t33/s2201"},"text":"section 2201 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
